  <brief_title>Proof of Concept Study for Safety and Efficacy of EDP239 in Hepatitis C Subjects</brief_title>
  <official_title>Double-Blind, Randomized, Placebo-controlled, Multi-center Trial to Determine the Safety and Antiviral Effect of Single Doses of EDP239 in Hepatitis C Virus (HCV) Infected Subjects</official_title>
