  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is, to assess whether EDP239 can reduce the HCV viral load in HCV
      gentotype-1 in chronically infected subjects and to further evaluate the safety profile of
      EDP239.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
